 and now used in no well-defined manner, partly even taken as synonymous wi=
th each other<sup id=3D"cite_ref-27" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https:/=
/en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fraction#cite_note-27"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">=
