numerator and denominator have the lowest <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.o=
rg/wiki/Absolute_value" title=3D"Absolute value">absolute values</a>. One s=
ays that the fraction has been reduced to its <i><a href=3D"https://en.wiki=
pedia.org/wiki/Lowest_terms" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Lowest terms">l=
owest terms</a></i>.
</p><p>If the numerator and the denominator do not share any factor greater=
