tfrac {3}{5}}\times {\tfrac {3}{3}}=3D{\tfrac {9}{15}}}"></span>=E2=81=A0</=
span>. Since <link rel=3D"mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href=3D"mw-data:Tem=
plateStyles:r1214402035"><span class=3D"sfrac">=E2=81=A0<span class=3D"tion=
"><span class=3D"num">3</span><span class=3D"sr-only">/</span><span class=
