m">3</span><span class=3D"sr-only">/</span><span class=3D"den">3</span></sp=
an>=E2=81=A0</span> does not change the value of the fraction.
</p><p>Second, convert <link rel=3D"mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href=3D"m=
